8e336fdb-c356-4a4a-8daa-23b1e2dfb48a.do_description: To make the output, you have to...use just grey blocks add blocks to the top of the blue box, add two up, and then two to the right. Below the blue box add grey blocks, two down and then two to the left. Repeat this pattern to the edge of the grid.
8e336fdb-c356-4a4a-8daa-23b1e2dfb48a.grid_description: The output grid size...is the same size.
8e336fdb-c356-4a4a-8daa-23b1e2dfb48a.see_description: In the input, you should see...a blue square.

96617f7e-6cda-4e4f-8e7e-9442e261df50.do_description: To make the output, you have to... put two light grey squares above the blue square. Then two more light grey squares to the right of the last square you added. Put another two grey squares going up, and continue this pattern until you reach the end of the grid. This will build a grey staircase pattern from the blue square to the upper right corner.Beginning at the blue square again, put two light grey squares going down. Then put two going left, then two down, and continue until you reach the end of the grid. This will build a grey staircase pattern from the blue square to the bottom left corner.
96617f7e-6cda-4e4f-8e7e-9442e261df50.grid_description: The output grid size... is the same as the input grid
96617f7e-6cda-4e4f-8e7e-9442e261df50.see_description: In the input, you should see... a blue square
